#### 1. In the same notebook for **Log Metric Anomaly Baselines**, after completing the DQL > Open the side menu with ... and select Open With
![diagram](data:image/png;base64,)
####     2. Open the Davis Anomaly Detector
####     3. Remove the following from the DQL Timeseries command `, value.A = avg(log.loglevelcounter.oteldemo, scalar: true) `
####     3. Select the Advanced Mode
####     4. Fill out the **Event details** as per your requirements in the bottom step
####     5. Check-out the GB scan size for DQL Query - it should be 0 bytes
![diagram](data:image/png;base64,)
####     6. Press Create to save
